    {"id": "file:fix.py", "type": "file", "name": "fix.py", "filePath": "fix.py", "summary": "修复流程的命令行入口点，读取诊断报告和配置文件，调用 FixAgent 执行代码修复，并打印 FixProposal 摘要。", "tags": ["入口点","cli","agent","修复流程"]},
    {"id": "file:src/agent/fix_agent.py", "type": "file", "name": "fix_agent.py", "filePath": "src/agent/fix_agent.py", "summary": "实现核心 FixAgent 类，通过 LangChain ReAct agent 编排 apply_fix、run_build、run_tests 等工具，自动完成代码修复并经历可重试的迭代循环，最终结果记录为 FixProposal。", "tags": ["agent","修复流程","LangChain","工具编排"]},
    {"id": "file:src/agent/fix_prompts.py", "type": "file", "name": "fix_prompts.py", "filePath": "src/agent/fix_prompts.py", "summary": "定义 FixAgent 使用的系统提示词，指导 LLM 按 ReAct 模式执行代码修复，约束其行为规范和约定。", "tags": ["提示词","LLM","agent","系统提示"]},
    {"id": "file:src/config.py", "type": "file", "name": "config.py", "filePath": "src/config.py", "summary": "定义项目运行时配置数据类 Config 和加载函数 load_config，从 YAML 文件读取 LLM 设置、目标项目目录等参数，支持环境变量覆盖 API key。", "tags": ["配置","数据模型","YAML配置"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/_command_runner.py", "type": "file", "name": "_command_runner.py", "filePath": "src/tools/_command_runner.py", "summary": "提供底层命令执行工具函数，包括 fix_id 格式校验、指定在工作目录中安全执行 shell 命令、超时处理和通用输出处理。", "tags": ["工具函数","命令执行","validation","底层工具"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/apply_fix.py", "type": "file", "name": "apply_fix.py", "filePath": "src/tools/apply_fix.py", "summary": "实现代码修复应用工具，通过工厂函数 make_apply_fix_tool 生成 LangChain 工具，支持精确行级编辑、路径安全校验、快照验证和工作区隔离（copy-on-write），修改文件并注释变更，原子持久化。", "tags": ["工具工厂","代码修复","文件操作","安全校验"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/run_build.py", "type": "file", "name": "run_build.py", "filePath": "src/tools/run_build.py", "summary": "提供 make_run_build_tool 工厂函数，在工作目录下执行 Maven 构建，封装为 LangChain 工具，将输出返回给 LLM agent。", "tags": ["工具工厂","构建工具","LangChain","Maven"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/run_tests.py", "type": "file", "name": "run_tests.py", "filePath": "src/tools/run_tests.py", "summary": "提供 make_run_tests_tool 工厂函数，在工作目录下执行测试并封装为 LangChain 工具，将测试结果返回给 LLM agent 作为修复验证依据。", "tags": ["工具工厂","测试工具","LangChain","验证"]},
    {"id": "file:src/agent/diagnosis_agent.py", "type": "file", "name": "diagnosis_agent.py", "filePath": "src/agent/diagnosis_agent.py", "summary": "实现诊断 agent，封装 LangGraph ReAct agent，装备 read_source / find_callers / submit_diagnosis 三类工具，对 Java 异常堆栈进行回溯分析、收集关键证据，最终将诊断报告写入 workspace/diagnosis/ 目录。", "tags": ["service","agent","entry-point","event-handler"]},
    {"id": "file:src/agent/prompts.py", "type": "file", "name": "prompts.py", "filePath": "src/agent/prompts.py", "summary": "为 DiagnosisAgent 构建系统提示词模板，将回溯算法流程、约束和策略整合到 LLM system prompt 字符串中。", "tags": ["utility","service"]},
    {"id": "file:src/source_index.py", "type": "file", "name": "source_index.py", "filePath": "src/source_index.py", "summary": "提供 Java 源文件索引功能，扫描 Maven 项目目录，建立类名到相对路径的映射，支持全名和短名两种查询方式。", "tags": ["utility","service","data-model"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/find_callers.py", "type": "file", "name": "find_callers.py", "filePath": "src/tools/find_callers.py", "summary": "提供 find_callers LangChain 工具的工厂模块：在 Java 源代码目录中全文搜索指定方法名的调用点，返回带行号的匹配结果列表，最多 20 条。", "tags": ["utility","tool-definition","api-handler"]},
    {"id": "file:src/tools/read_source.py", "type": "file", "name": "read_source.py", "filePath": "src/tools/read_source.py", "summary": "提供 read_source LangChain 工具的工厂模块：通过 SourceIndex 将类名解析为路径，并读取指定行范围的 Java 源码片段并带行号返回。", "tags": ["utility","tool-definition","api-handler"]},
    {"id": "file:diagnose.py", "type": "file", "name": "diagnose.py", "filePath": "diagnose.py", "summary": "系统主诊断脚本的命令行入口，读取堆栈文件和配置，构建 Java 源码索引，启动 DiagnosisAgent 完成根因分析，结果写入 JSON 报告文件。", "tags": ["入口点","agent","根因","诊断流程"]},
    {"id": "file:src/models.py", "type": "file", "name": "models.py", "filePath": "src/models.py", "summary": "定义项目全局共享数据模型（dataclass），包括堆栈帧、证据和目标位置、数据层采集、诊断报告、修复方案等，贯穿诊断和修复流程的数据契约。", "tags": ["数据模型","schema-definition","type-definition","核心"]},
    {"id": "file:src/report_writer.py", "type": "file", "name": "report_writer.py", "filePath": "src/report_writer.py", "summary": "提供诊断报告输出工具：`print_summary` 将 DiagnosisReport 格式化打印到控制台，`write_json` 将报告序列化为 JSON 文件写入磁盘。", "tags": ["工具函数","输出","序列化","核心"]},
    {"id": "file:src/stack_parser.py", "type": "file", "name": "stack_parser.py", "filePath": "src/stack_parser.py", "summary": "提供 Java 异常堆栈文本的解析工具：`parse_stack_trace` 使用正则将文本转换为 StackFrame 列表，`find_business_top_frame` 过滤框架包位置，找到业务层栈帧。", "tags": ["工具函数","堆栈解析","解析","核心"]},
    {"id": "file:commit_fix.py", "type": "file", "name": "commit_fix.py", "filePath": "commit_fix.py", "summary": "修复流程的最终命令行脚本，读取修复方案和诊断报告、调用 FixAgent 生成代码修改、校验冲突，并通过 SVN 提交变更，同时支持 dry-run 和对话式测试。", "tags": ["入口点","agent","修复流程","svn","cli"]},
    {"id": "file:src/commit/patcher.py", "type": "file", "name": "patcher.py", "filePath": "src/commit/patcher.py", "summary": "提供文件修改管理的工具集：路径安全校验、修改前哈希快照、SVN 更新后冲突检测、精确行级编辑原子写入，以及生成 unified diff 以供后续审查。", "tags": ["工具函数","补丁","冲突检测","diff","原子写入"]},
    {"id": "file:src/commit/svn.py", "type": "file", "name": "svn.py", "filePath": "src/commit/svn.py", "summary": "封装核心 SVN 命令行操作：svn update（拉取最新版本）、svn commit（提交并返回版本号）、svn revert（还原文件列表，支持未修改），均通过 subprocess 调用，失败时抛出 RuntimeError。", "tags": ["svn","工具函数","版本控制","subprocess"]},
